Quick instructions for NTRUEncrypt

- NtruEncrypt.generateKeyPair() generates an encryption key pair
- EncryptionKeyPair.priv.getEncoded() and EncryptionKeyPair.pub.getEncoded() convert the generated keys to byte arrays
- EncryptionPrivateKey(byte[], EncryptionParameters) and EncryptionPublicKey(byte[], EncryptionParameters) convert a byte array to a key
- NtruEncrypt.encrypt() and NtruEncrypt.decrypt() for encryption/decryption


Quick instructions for NTRUSign

- NtruSign.generateKeyPair() generates an encryption key pair
- SignaturePrivateKey.getEncoded() and SignaturePublicKey.getEncoded() convert the generated keys to byte arrays
- SignaturePrivateKey(byte[], SignatureParameters) and SignaturePublicKey(byte[], SignatureParameters) convert a byte array to a key
- NtruSign.sign() and NtruSign.verify() for signing/verification
